## ğŸš€ Setup Instructions

### 1. Database Setup
```sql
-- Run the SQL schema file
source oop-database-schema.sql

-- Or manually in MySQL Workbench:
-- Copy and execute the entire schema
```

### 2. Update DBConnection.java
```java
private static final String PASSWORD = "YOUR_MYSQL_PASSWORD";
```

### 3. Compile and Run
```bash
# Compile all files
javac -d bin --module-path /path/to/javafx-sdk/lib --add-modules javafx.controls AMS/*.java

# Run
java --module-path /path/to/javafx-sdk/lib --add-modules javafx.controls -cp bin AMS.Main
```

